s.newInstance(...)`\\n- `ReflectUtils.findDeclaredMethod(...)`\\n- `ReflectUtils.addAllMethods(...)`\\n- `ReflectUtils.findInterfaceMethod(...)`\\n- `ReflectUtils.defineClass(...)`, with Native Image unsupported dynamic class loading handled via `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`\\n\\nAlso added `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED` for JVM tests and native-image build args so cglib can access `ClassLoader#defineClass`.\\n\\nTests were not run, per instruction.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0bce82438a9b6c150169f73944151881969197f191a85fb12f\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1140, \"output\": 357, \"cacheRead\": 45056, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 46553, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777809728068, \"responseId\": \"resp_0bce82438a9b6c150169f73940a0f881968b4cde716f51139c\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
